external_knowledge:
- "rooted in the soil of the 20th century and beyond" refers to parties founded after 1900;
- "sowing their ideological seeds among the young" metaphorically refers to the parties' involvement with voters in the 18-24 age group;
- "flourishing in ongoing elections" means the election is currently live;
- "nurtured by the golden rain of donations" refers to the source of funding being donations.

